componentStorage.title: P1 will spin again if T1 > this number
Plot of times each player won

componentStorage.text:
The Games collection contains 1000 simulated games. If player 1 gets a number larger than the slider (Largest) on the first spin (P1_T1), player 1 stops. Otherwise spin again. The plot above shows the number each player won out of the 1000 games.

Hover over each column name to learn how the simulation is constructed. Click on the ruler menu of "Simulated games of Showcase Showdown," then "rerandomize all" to run a new simulation of the game.

What integer value of Largest is best for player 1?
